### ============================================================
### query-burst-msa member-service API
### Base URL: http://localhost:18114
### ============================================================

# @no-log

### Health
GET http://localhost:18114/actuator/health

### ============================================================
### [DATA INIT]
### ============================================================

### 테스트 데이터 적재 시작
POST http://localhost:18114/api/data-init

### 테스트 데이터 적재 상태 확인
GET http://localhost:18114/api/data-init/status

### ============================================================
### [MEMBER]
### ============================================================

### 회원 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:18114/api/members?size=20

### 회원 목록 조회 - 다음 페이지
GET http://localhost:18114/api/members?cursor=1000&size=20

### 회원 생성
POST http://localhost:18114/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "msa-user@example.com",
  "name": "홍길동",
  "grade": "VIP",
  "region": "SEOUL"
}

### 회원 수정
PATCH http://localhost:18114/api/members/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "김개발",
  "grade": "VVIP",
  "region": "BUSAN"
}

### 회원 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:18114/api/members/1
